### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiKey = your-api-key-from-env
@recipientPhone = +919876543210

### Banner
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health/live

### Health (DB + Redis)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health

### Send a free-form text (only inside 24h customer-care window)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/messages/send/text
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "to": "{{recipientPhone}}",
  "text": "Hello from Prodaxis test"
}

### Send the hello_world template
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/messages/send/template
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "to": "{{recipientPhone}}",
  "template_name": "hello_world",
  "language_code": "en_US"
}

### List recent messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/messages?page=1&page_size=20
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Sync templates from Meta to local DB
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/templates/sync
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{}

### List local templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/templates
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Create a campaign (draft)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "name": "Test Campaign",
  "template_name": "hello_world",
  "language_code": "en_US"
}

### List campaigns
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/campaigns
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Tenants
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
